              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37536537/" class="">诸葛亮《与兄瑾论白帝兵书》辨误</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1240031/" class=" " title="信而好古">信而好古</a>
                (雪上空留马行处。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37536537">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37536537/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p37536537-6.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-04-08 10:03</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p37536537-6.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p37536537-2.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
